# Backend — inverted whitelist (inherited from root)
# --------------------------------------------------
# `data/`, `__pycache__/`, `.pytest_cache/`, etc. are left un-whitelisted
# and therefore excluded automatically by the leading `*`.

*

!.gitignore

# Python source + build/test config (at any depth)
!**/*.py
!*.ini
!*.txt
!*.toml

# Subdirectories — git needs these un-ignored to descend into them.
# Files inside are filtered by the rules above (**/*.py etc.).
!routers/
!services/
!repositories/
!tests/
